ayush1325: What is a link property? Do you mean `links` which seems to allow pointing to a label? I guess what you are suggesting is something like the following:
```dts
&main_uart6 {
  links = <&cc1352_uart>;
  ...
}

&cc1352 {
   cc1352_uart {
     compatibile = "something";
   }
  ...
}
```
